80) Build a test cookie with the setcookie( ) function using PHP. 
<?php 
// Set a test cookie named "test_cookie" 
setcookie("test_cookie", "This is a test", time() + 3600, "/"); // Expires in 1 hour 
?> 
<!DOCTYPE html> 
<html> 
<head> 
<title>Test Cookie</title> 
</head> 
<body> 
<h2>Testing Cookie with setcookie()</h2> 
<?php 
if (isset($_COOKIE['test_cookie'])) { 
echo "   
. "</strong>"; 
} else { 
echo "       
Cookie is set. Value: <strong>" . htmlspecialchars($_COOKIE['test_cookie']) 
Cookie not available yet. Please <a href=''>refresh the page</a>."; 
} 
?> 
</body> 
</html> 
